'''[[Senator/Legends|Senator]] Jheramahd Greyshade''' was a [[Human/Legends|Human]] [[Gender/Legends|male]] who represented the [[Commonality]] in the [[Galactic Senate/Legends|Galactic Senate]] of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Republic]].

==Biography==
In [[23 BBY/Legends|23 BBY]], he was assassinated by [[Tsian]], who, upon killing him in his apartment, threw his corpse off the roof of [[500 Republica/Legends|''500 Republica'']], shortly before a critical vote on the [[Financial Reform Act]], which he supported. His body fell to the Coruscant streets, which caused a massive and fatal pile up. He was succeeded in office by his cousin, [[Simon Greyshade/Legends|Simon]].

